  "instructions": [
    "Marinate the beef strips in a mixture of soy sauce, lime juice, garlic, ginger, and aji amarillo peppers for at least 2 hours",
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees",
    "Remove the beef from the marinade and cook in a Korean brass bowl with vegetable oil for 5 minutes",
    "Add the marinade to the bowl and cook for an additional 10 minutes",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste",
    "Serve the beef hot in the Korean brass bowl",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh cilantro and scallions",
    "Serve with steamed rice or roasted vegetables for a filling meal"
